# ====================================================================================================================================
# BATCH 1 - MAPS + SIM + LETTERS
# Modernised BISS Staff E2E regression packs. One legacy Feature -> one file, one chained E2E
# Scenario, with # SECTION markers mapping back to the original AT-TC ids.
#
# Data handling:
#   - Herd / parcel / reference values are resolved from the DB at runtime by the @staffdata
#     hook via DBRouter, and exposed as Hooks.STAFF_HERD / STAFF_PARCEL / STAFF_REF lists.
#     No Excel round-trip, no "from row N" references in step text.
#   - Staff agent accounts stay hardcoded in the feature (agr11612 / agr4442 / agr2332),
#     as they are permission fixtures, not test data.
#   - Password resolved from TestData.xlsx "Password" column via the TD: mechanism.
#   - URL launched by Hooks from the Config sheet.
#
# Step definitions : StaffSteps.java (stepdefinitions.STAFF)
# Locators         : ObjectRepository.properties - Staff sections
# Author           : Aniket Pathare | aniket.pathare@government.ie
# Created          : 15-07-2026
# ====================================================================================================================================


